---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SMS Terms & Conditions - Always Open" description="Always Open SMS Terms & Conditions. Program description, message frequency, rates, and opt-out instructions.">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>SMS Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="hero-meta">Effective date: May 28, 2026 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Always Open / openalways.io</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <main>
    <section>
      <h2>Program Name</h2>
      <p>Always Open SMS Notifications.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Program Description</h2>
      <p>Always Open operates an AI-powered answering and lead capture service for small businesses. As part of that service, we send SMS text notifications to business clients, including lead and inquiry alerts, appointment information, and service follow-ups. Messages are sent only to clients and authorized business contacts who have opted in.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
      <p>Message frequency varies based on inbound call volume — typically 1–5 messages per day.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Cost</h2>
      <p><strong>Message and data rates may apply.</strong> Always Open does not charge for these messages; standard rates from your mobile carrier may apply.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>How to Opt Out</h2>
      <p>You may opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any SMS message. After you reply STOP, you will receive one confirmation message and no further texts. To opt back in, reply <strong>START</strong> or contact us directly.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Help</h2>
      <p>For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message, or email us at the address below.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>Your information is handled in accordance with our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. We do not sell or share your phone number with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="callout">
        <p><strong>Always Open</strong></p>
        <p>Questions about these Terms or your messages?</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@openalways.io">hello@openalways.io</a></p>
        <p>Website: <a href="https://openalways.io">openalways.io</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
<style>
  .hero { background: var(--navy); padding: 72px 48px 56px; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--amber); }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--amber); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(36px,5vw,52px); color: #fff; line-height: 1.15; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .hero-meta { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight: 400; margin: 0; }
  main { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 48px 96px; }
  section { margin-bottom: 52px; padding-bottom: 52px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  section:last-child { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; }
  h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border-left: 3px solid var(--amber); }
  p { color: var(--body); margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 300; }
  p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 14px 0; }
  ul li { padding: 8px 0 8px 24px; position: relative; color: var(--body); font-weight: 300; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  ul li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 17px; width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--sage); border-radius: 50%; }
  .callout { background: var(--navy); color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 28px 32px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .callout p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 15px; }
  .callout p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .callout strong { color: var(--amber); font-weight: 500; }
  .callout a { color: var(--amber); border-bottom-color: var(--amber); }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .hero { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; } main { padding: 40px 24px 64px; } }
</style>
